%description
MoveIt plugins for the Fanuc M-20iA / ARC Mate 120iC (and variants). This
package contains plugins for use with MoveIt and Fanuc M-20iA / ARC Mate 120iC
manipulators. Plugins included support the base and 10L model. See the Fanuc
M-20iA support package for information on used joint angle and velocity limits.
Before using any of the plugins included in this package, be sure to check they
are correct for the particular robot model and configuration you intend to use
them with. Contributors: This package has received contributions from: Joe
Spanier (M-20iA/10L IKFast).

%prep
